===Etymology===
Named for the type locality in the [[Andes]] Mountains.

===Noun===
'''andesine'''
# {{mineralogy}} [[sodium]] [[calcium]] [[aluminum]] [[silicate]], (<math>Na_xCa_xAlSi_3O_8</math>), a [[plagioclase]] [[feldspar]], the third member of the albite-anorthite [[solid solution]] series. Found in fine-grained [[andesite]] lavas; [[crystal]]s are rarely seen.

